    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox delivering power to the rear wheels via a variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the communicative steering and lateral grip these chassis are renowned for. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. While the exterior shows honest road wear, the drivetrain remains robust with linear power delivery and precise gear synchronization. A purist\u2019s spec optimized for performance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
